

JNDI Name: jdbc/Park
Persistence unit name: JpaPUPark
Table generate strategi: Drop and Table
pool name: derby-park

Persistence Provider: EclipseLink ( JPA2.1 )

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
List the parks
GET
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add new park
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park
{   
	"name":"FantasticPark",
        "postCode":"1098",
        "country":"HUN",
        "city":"Budapest",
        "street":"Fo utca",
        "streetNumber":"34",
        "money":123456,
        "area":1000,
        "priceOfTicket":2000
}
<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add new machine
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/machine
{
	"fantasiaName":"SuperGokart",
	"sizeOfMachine":400,
	"priceOfTicket":500,
	"maxCapacity":30,
	"sellingPrice":20000;
	"type":"GOKART",
	"minimumAge":"14"
}

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add machine to park
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/2/addmachine/1
The first the park id and the second is the machine id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Remove machine from park
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/2/removemachine/1
The first the park id and the second is the machine id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Add visitor
POST
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor
{
	"name":"TestVisitor",
	"state":"REST",
	"money":50000,
	"dateOfBirth":"1992-04-23T22:22:22.75+02:00",
	"isActive":"false"
}
<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Get visitors
GET
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor


<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Login visitor to park
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/logintopark/1/park/1
The first is the visitor id and the second is the park id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Exit visitor from park
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/exitfrompark/1/park/1
The first si the visitor id and the second is the park id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Visitor board the machine
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/boardtomachine/1/machine/1
The first is the visitor id and the second is the park id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Visitor unboard the machine
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/unboardtomachine/1/machine/1
The first is the visitor id and the second is the park id

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Visitor read to guestBook
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/writetobook/3/park/2
The first is the visitor id and the second is the park id
Content-Type: text/plain
Content: This was a fantastic expreience!

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Remove park
DELETE
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/deletepark/1

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Update park
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/park/updatepark/1
{   
	"name":"BudapestiVidampark",
        "postCode":"1111",
        "country":"HUN",
        "city":"Budapest",
        "street":"Varosliget utca",
        "streetNumber":"22",
        "money":0,
        "area":10000,
        "priceOfTicket":3000
}
<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Remove visitor
DELETE
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/deletevisitor/1
{
	"name":"Aladar",
	"state":"REST",
	"money":2000,
	"dateOfBirth":"1998-01-23T22:22:22.75+02:00",
	"isActive":"false"
}

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Update visitor
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/visitor/updatevisitor/1

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Remove machine
DELETE
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/machine/deletemachine/1

<<<<<<<<------------------------------------------------->>>>>>>>>>>>
Update machine
PUT
http://localhost:8080/AmusementPark-web/machine/updatemachine/1
{
	"fantasiaName":"Swing",
	"sizeOfMachine":30,
	"priceOfTicket":400,
	"maxCapacity":100,
	"sellingPrice"12000;
	"type":"SWING",
	"minimumAge":"6"
}




